# MyInspector .gitignore
#
# Repo is PUBLIC (SerranoJ3/myinspector on GitHub). Anything committed
# becomes searchable. Buddy/CC use .coordination/ as a working file channel,
# so some operational scratch files live there but should NEVER ship public.
#
# Patterns below cover known-sensitive files and future similar ones.
# Files stay on Jorge's local disk for Buddy + CC to read; they just don't
# travel to GitHub.

# ── Operational / personal scratch (Buddy + CC working notes) ────────────────
.coordination/buddy_context*.md
.coordination/end_of_day_*.md
.coordination/progress_report_*.md
.coordination/velocity_analytics_*.md

# ── Security details (super_admin email, attack-surface inventories) ─────────
.coordination/SUNDAY_SECURITY_AUDIT*.md

# ── Demo seed spec (names real demo target + sanitization-list-as-leak) ──────
.coordination/MI-DEMO_seed_spec_*.md

# ── NJAW operational data (contractor-territory map from internal source) ────
.coordination/MI402_TOWNS_CONTRACTORS_REFERENCE_BRIEF.md
.coordination/work_order_MI402_towns_contractors.md

# ── Real-prospect identifying material (Jeff + employer + credential) ────────
.coordination/MI404_HERALD_TAB_BRIEF.md
.coordination/work_order_MI404_herald_tab.md

# ── Firm code rotation (rotation notes + migrations contain live signup secrets) ─
.coordination/buddy_firm_code_rotation*.md
supabase/migrations/*rotate*firm*code*.sql

# ── Standard noise ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
node_modules/
*.log
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
